{"tid":2446543,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"原來小米政治立場咁黃的 以後唔反了~","createTime":"2021-03-14T13:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T07:17:51.000Z","uid":392766,"like":16,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e106f150269b4e16f3663221ef665426f54beed0","tid":2446543,"uid":392766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"反修例運動初期，小米已經暗示自己同香港人企埋同一陣線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAzmc24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAzmc24.jpg&h=4c2507fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，小米喺微博同樣不畏強權，直接寫出「五大平台，缺一不可」嘅口號。最後仲搞到滿城風雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6VSSjJv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6VSSjJv.jpg&h=e23ae598&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來就好黃嘅小米，就畀大家一步步推向藍營，如下圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/od5Mpba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fod5Mpba.jpg&h=4876a6ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要有巴打專登去小米之家影後生仔相，放上連登公審佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我決定唔盲反了，聽日即刻去小米之家預訂返幾部小米11支持呢間公司了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c114b71d7c7513ffb71fa4c81eb0e136e6385889","tid":2446543,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:49:30.000Z","msg":"聽日是咪大爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0a887c49f1ed69bcfe6f9bdb6dd2311588c9a6","tid":2446543,"uid":10277,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:50:35.000Z","msg":"哭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89caa8c5e4ee19d1ab8446a2bfe01cd388fd3690","tid":2446543,"uid":392766,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"咁多位手足，聽日大家一齊上小米之家，一人買一部小米11懲罰下小米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4ee1db35c9c3729903ed4bfc212f5fbcab810f","tid":2446543,"uid":392766,"like":32,"dislike":7,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"9a0a887c49f1ed69bcfe6f9bdb6dd2311588c9a6","tid":2446543,"uid":10277,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:50:35.000Z","msg":"哭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jrRvQTw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjrRvQTw.png&h=b54b191d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c52fbe76427352f85b5980ff5025349115e707a","tid":2446543,"uid